powers: Egghead is a synthetic being and can shift his density at will, either becoming completely intangible or partially materializing within another individual, causing them immense pain. He can also download data into a human or computer brain merely by touch.
significantissues: First time in action and confronted by Young Avengers (Dark Reign: Young Avengers #1, 2009)
potentially offered a place on Young Avengers (Dark Reign: Young Avengers #2, 2009) partnered with Vision as part of recruiting session (Dark Reign: Young Avengers #3, 2009)
declined membership into Young Avengers and told them the Enchantress' secret (Dark Reign: Young Avengers #4, 2009)
rematch with Young Avengers and escaped with teammates (Dark Reign: Young Avengers #5, 2009)
